entry.string: INSERT INTO db.Putnik (ImePut,PrezimePut,JMBGPut, BrojPasosa,KontaktPut, AdresaPut, mailPut) VALUES (#[payload.ImePut],#[payload.PrezimePut],#[payload.JMBGPut],#[payload.BrojPasosa],#[payload.KontaktPut],#[payload.AdresaPut],#[payload.mailPut])

INSERT INTO db.Putnik (ImePut,PrezimePut,JMBGPut, BrojPasosa,KontaktPut, AdresaPut, mailPut) VALUES (#[payload.ImePut],#[payload.PrezimePut],#[payload.JMBGPut],#[payload.BrojPasosa],#[payload.KontaktPut],#[payload.AdresaPut],#[payload.mailPut])

Select a.AvionskaKartaID,a.CenaKarte,a.DatumKupovine,a.CheckIn,a.BrojSedista,a.LetID,l.DatumPolaska,l.VremePolaska,l.Status,l.Terminal,l.SlobodnoBizKlasa,l.SlobodnoEkoKlasa,l.AvionID,l.KompanijaID,l.DestinacijaID,l.PilotID,a.KlasaID,k.TipKlase,a.PutnikID,p.ImePut,p.PrezimePut,p.JMBGPut,p.BrojPasosa,p.KontaktPut,p.AdresaPut,p.mailPut from db.AvionskaKarta as a inner join db.Let as l on (a.LetID=l.LetID) inner join db.Klasa as k on (k.klasaID=a.KlasaID) inner join db.Putnik as p on (p.PutnikID=a.PutnikID)
SELECT * from db.Putnik where ImePut like '%#[message.inboundProperties.'http.query.params'.search]%'

SELECT l.LetID ,l.DatumPolaska, l.VremePolaska, l.Status, l.Terminal , l.SlobodnoBizKlasa, l.SlobodnoEkoKlasa,l.AvionID,a.Marka,a.Model,a.UkupnoBizKlasa,a.UkupnoEkoKlasa,l.KompanijaID, k.NazivAK,l.DestinacijaID,d.NazivAerodroma,d.Grad,l.PilotID,p.ImeP,p.PrezimeP,p.JMBGP,p.KontaktP,p.AdresaP,p.mail from db.Let as l inner join db.Avion as a on (a.AvionID=l.AvionID) inner join db.Destinacija as d on (l.DestinacijaID=d.DestinacijaID) inner join db.AvioKompanija as k on (k.KompanijaID=l.KompanijaID) inner join db.Pilot as p on (p.PilotID=l.PilotID)

Select a.AvionskaKartaID,a.CenaKarte,a.DatumKupovine,a.CheckIn,a.BrojSedista,a.LetID,l.DatumPolaska,l.VremePolaska,l.VremeSletanja,l.Status,l.Terminal,l.SlobodnoBizKlasa,l.SlobodnoEkoKlasa,l.AvionID,l.KompanijaID,l.DestinacijaID,l.PilotID,a.KlasaID,k.TipKlase,a.PutnikID,p.ImePut,p.PrezimePut,p.JMBGPut,p.BrojPasosa,p.KontaktPut,p.AdresaPut,p.mailPut from db.AvionskaKarta as a inner join db.Let as l on (a.LetID=l.LetID) inner join db.Klasa as k on (k.klasaID=a.KlasaID) inner join db.Putnik as p on (p.PutnikID=a.PutnikID)

SELECT l.LetID ,l.DatumPolaska, l.VremePolaska, l.Status, l.Terminal , l.SlobodnoBizKlasa, l.SlobodnoEkoKlasa,l.AvionID,a.Marka,a.Model,a.UkupnoBizKlasa,a.UkupnoEkoKlasa,l.AvioKompanijaID, k.NazivAK,l.DestinacijaID,d.NazivAerodroma,d.Grad,l.PilotID,p.ImeP,p.PrezimeP,p.JMBGP,p.KontaktP,p.AdresaP,p.mail from db.Let as l inner join db.Avion as a on (a.AvionID=l.AvionID) inner join db.Destinacija as d on (l.DestinacijaID=d.DestinacijaID) inner join db.AvioKompanija as k on (k.KompanijaID=l.KompanijaID) inner join db.Pilot as p on (p.PilotID=l.PilotID)
SELECT * from db.Putnik where ImePut like %#[message.inboundProperties.'http.query.params'.search]% or PrezimePut like %#[message.inboundProperties.'http.query.params'.search]%
SELECT * from db.Putnik where ime like '%#[message.inboundProperties.'http.query.params'.search]%'

UPDATE db.Putnik set ImePut= '#[payload.ImePut]', PrezimePut= '#[payload.PrezimePut]', JMBGPut= #[payload.JMBGPut], BrojPasosa= '#[payload.BrojPasosa]', KontaktPut= '#[payload.KontaktPut]', AdresaPut= '#[payload.AdresaPut]', mailPut= '#[payload.mailPut]' where PutnikID=#[message.inboundProperties.'http.uri.params'.id]

UPDATE db.Pilot set ImeP= '#[payload.ImeP]', PrezimeP= '#[payload.PrezimeP]', JMBGP= #[payload.JMBGP], KontaktP= '#[payload.KontaktP]', AdresaP= '#[payload.AdresaP]', mail= '#[payload.mail]' where PilotID=#[message.inboundProperties.'http.uri.params'.id]

UPDATE db.Putnik set ImePut= '#[payload.ImePut]', PrezimePut= '#[payload.PrezimePut]', JMBGPut= #[payload.JMBGPut], BrojPasosa= '#[payload.BrojPasosa]', KontaktPut= '#[payload.KontaktPut]', AdresaPut= '#[payload.AdresaPut]', mailPut= '#[payload.mailPut]' where PutnikID=#[message.inboundProperties.'http.uri.params'.id]
